	<div id="denim-dilemmas" class="two-col">
		<h2>Denim <span class="desktop">&mdash;&mdash;</span> Dilemmas</h2>
		<p class="">Our resident denim expert, Wanda Rivets (wink, wink), has a solution to every style quandary.</p>
		<div class="col">
			<img src="/b/fashion/images/projects/denim/denim-styles/editorial-4.jpg" alt=""/>
			<p><strong>Q.</strong> Dear Wanda Rivets: I love my pearl-embellished jeans—but sitting in them, not so much. How do I keep my bejeweled pairs from leaving me in bruises? <strong>—Uncomfortable in Miami</strong></p>
			<p><strong>A.</strong> Dear Uncomfortable: We adore the luminous look of those semiprecious pairs! First, try favoring styles that cluster heavy embellishments on the front so you won't feel them when you sit. If your jeans do have back-pocket bling, seek out upholstered seating like plush banquettes or a padded cushion so embellishments can sink into the giving fabric—rather than your leg. Dining alfresco? Skip café chairs with perforated, open-weave designs like cane, rattan or wire where precious pearls can get caught in openings, to ensure your prized pairs stay pristine—and you won't get trapped in your seat.</p>
			<a href="https://www.bloomingdales.com/shop/womens-apparel/jeans/Jean_trends/Embellished?id=5545">shop embellished denim</a>
		</div>
		<div class="col">
			<img src="/b/fashion/images/projects/denim/denim-styles/editorial-5.jpg" alt=""/>
			<p><strong>Q.</strong> Dear Wanda Rivets: I'm dying to get a pair of fringed-hem jeans, but at only 5'2", how do I ensure I'm not mopping up the streets with that fabulously frayed flare? <strong>—Petite but Persistent in Dayton</strong></p>
			<p>A. Dear Persistent: For most folks, cropped flares should hit right above the ankle. If you want to go a bit higher, we find the most flattering look of all is cropped just enough to show some shin at the smallest place where your leg starts to narrow. To help even more with height, try pairing them with a block-heel style that will really get your fringe in the stylish swing of things.</p>
			<a href="https://www.bloomingdales.com/shop/womens-apparel/jeans/Jean_trends/Statement%20Hems?id=5545">shop statement hems</a>
		</div>
	</div>

