				<h3>Denim-on-Denim</h3>
				<hr class="splitter"/>
				<p><strong>Do:</strong> Experiment with washes. The point is to be matchy-matchy, but break up the monotony by mixing lighter and darker shades—even if it's subtle, like in this Levi's look.</p>
				<p><strong>Don't:</strong> Use cowboys as your outfit inspo. Full-on denim can naturally read Western, so opt for modern accessories (or none at all) to stay clean and current rather than costumey.</p>
				<a href="https://www.bloomingdales.com/shop/womens-apparel/jeans?id=5545">Shop Jeans</a>
