				<h3>Velvet All Day</h3>
				<hr class="splitter"/>
				<p><strong>Do:</strong> Opt for a colorful velvet jean rather than black, which instantly reads formal, and play with contrasting textures like cozy knits or poplin tops to keep the look casually cool.</p>
				<p><strong>Don't:</strong> Go overboard with embellished accessories, silky tops or sparkly jewelry  that can appear more party-ready than boardroom-bound during office hours. </p>
				<a href="https://www.bloomingdales.com/shop/womens-apparel/jeans/Jean_trends/Velvet?id=5545">Shop velvet jeans</a>
